13 for:
14 (1) reporting an incidence of workplace violence;
15 (2) seeking assistance or intervention from the hospital, hospital
16 security, law enforcement, or any other appropriate entity; or
17 (3) participating or refusing to participate in an investigation of
18 workplace violence.
19 (d)(1) A hospital shall post a notice in a conspicuous location, either
